item.title: CVE-2023-33993|2024-10-10T19:08:03.270Z -- sap_se -- sap%20business%20one%20%28b1i%20layer%29
item.description: B1i module of SAP Business One - version 10.0, application allows an authenticated user with deep knowledge to send crafted queries over the network to read or modify the SQL data. On successful exploitation, the attacker can cause high impact on confidentiality, integrity and availability of the application.
